sequenceDiagram
    participant O as 订单消费者
    participant P as PostgreSQL
    participant X as Outbox Relay
    participant M as RocketMQ
    participant C as 补偿消费者
    participant R as Redis

    O->>P: 订单失败事务
    Note over P: reservation=ORDER_REJECTED
    Note over P: 插入compensation_task和Outbox
    P-->>O: COMMIT

    X->>M: RESERVATION_COMPENSATE_REQUIRED
    M->>C: 投递补偿消息

    C->>P: CAS ORDER_REJECTED→COMPENSATING
    P-->>C: 成功
    C->>R: Lua条件恢复库存
    R-->>C: APPLIED或ALREADY_APPLIED
    C->>P: COMPENSATING→COMPENSATED
    C-->>M: ACK
